---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Podcast
nav_label: Investigate
permalink: /podcast/
intro: Listen in as we follow clues, stories, questions, and deeper trails from the world of Unschool Discoveries.
---

<section class="panel">

  <h2>The podcast trail</h2>

  <p class="lead">
    <strong>Investigate</strong> is the listening side of <em>Unschool Discoveries</em>.
  </p>

  <p>
    This is where we slow down, follow the clues, and talk through the ideas hiding inside the stories —
    curiosity, family life, nature, creativity, learning, and the strange little questions that turn into bigger discoveries.
  </p>


  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Episode notes and deeper trails</h2>

    <p>
      Each episode connects back to a deeper trail on (<strong>Unschool Pages</strong>){{site.unschoolPagesUrl}},
      where notes, references, resources, and behind-the-scenes thoughts keep growing with you input.
    </p><a class="button button-primary" href="{{ site.unschoolPagesUrl }}">Visit Unschool Pages</a>

  </section>

  <h2 id="episodes">Episodes</h2>

  {% if podcast.length %}
  <p>
    <strong>{{ podcast.length }} episodes available.</strong>
  </p>

  <div class="episode-list">
    {% for episode in podcast %}
    <article class="card episode-card">
      <div class="episode-card_left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Podcast Episode {{ episode.episodeNumber }}</p>

        {% if episode.image %}
        <img
          class="episode-card__image"
          src="{{ episode.image }}"
          alt=""
          loading="lazy">
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="episode-card__content">

        <h3>{{ episode.title }}</h3>

        <p class="episode-meta">
          {% if episode.dateLabel %}{{ episode.dateLabel }}{% endif %}
          {% if episode.duration %} · {{ episode.duration }}{% endif %}
        </p>

        {% if episode.description %}
        <p>{{ episode.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        <audio controls preload="none">
          <source
            src="{{ episode.audioUrl }}"
            {% if episode.audioType %}type="{{ episode.audioType }}" {% endif %}>
          Your browser does not support the audio element.
        </audio>


      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p>No podcast episodes found yet.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <p>
    Each episode is a trail. Some trails begin in the book. Some begin in real life.
    Some lead straight into the living notebook.
  </p>

  <div class="actions">
    <a class="button" href="#episodes">Start listening</a>
    <a class="button button-secondary" href="{{ site.unschoolPagesUrl }}">Visit Unschool Pages</a>
  </div>
</section>